Title: Fixed escaped HTML entities in view columns
Level: 1
Component: reporting
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
State: unknown
Version: 1.5.0b1
Date: 1519133099

When creating a PDF report which contains a view element. The columns
in this view could contain HTML escaped special characters like "&amp;quot;".
These signs are now displayed correctly in the PDF export.
